GET http://localhost:8000/

###
GET http://localhost:8000/health
###

GET http://localhost:8000/servers


### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "supersecretpassword"
}

###

### Login — copy the access_token and refresh_token from the response
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "supersecretpassword"
}

###

### Access protected route — paste your access_token here
GET http://localhost:8000/servers
Authorization: Bearer <paste_access_token_here>

###

### Refresh — paste your refresh_token here
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refresh_token": "<paste_refresh_token_here>"
}

###

### Logout — paste both tokens
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer <paste_access_token_here>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refresh_token": "<paste_refresh_token_here>"
}